data.description: Welcome to this two-story 3 Bedroom, 2 Bath home, situated on 10+/- Acres in Eastern Leon County that blends modern convenience with country charm.  The large wrap-around screened porch is the perfect place to relax, enjoy the peace and quiet of country life, and see abundant wildlife on the property.  Or, if you prefer take a dip in the pool or enjoy the hot tub.  Once you cross the threshold, you will be greeted by the charm of this house.  You will see hardwood, brick, and tile floors downstairs, and laminate vinyl plank (LVP) floors upstairs.  The kitchen features ample cabinetry, an island sink, ceramic top range and oven, a microwave oven range hood, a side-by-side refrigerator with ice and water in the door, and a pantry closet.  Three fireplaces are found in the house:  one in the living room, one in the den/study, and  one in the primary bedroom.  On the back side of the house, you will find a storage shed with two extended shed roofs, one on each side.  The property behind the shed is currently kept in its natural state.  Panther creek traverses the northeastern corner of the property.   The house and property are full of potential.  Come see for yourself.
